citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1 pm on 04 Apr
2023. Knocked on door, honked horn, waited 25 minutes, a person came by and said licensee wasn't home, left flyer.
End Section
